---
// Dedicated vs Shared Gateway Role — static SVG viz (no client JS)
---
<figure class="fm-gateway-role" aria-label="Two gateway configurations compared: dedicated node versus shared repeater-gateway">
  <div class="fm-gr-wrap">
    <div class="fm-gr-option">
      <div class="fm-gr-label">Dedicated gateway</div>
      <div class="fm-gr-device fm-gr-gateway">
        <span class="fm-gr-icon">⌛</span>
        <span class="fm-gr-name">Gateway node</span>
        <div class="fm-gr-roles">
          <span class="fm-gr-role fm-gr-active">WiFi → MQTT</span>
          <span class="fm-gr-role fm-gr-inactive">RF relay</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fm-gr-arrow">↓</div>
      <div class="fm-gr-broker">MQTT broker</div>
      <div class="fm-gr-note">One job: bridge the mesh to the internet. Placed where WiFi is good.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fm-gr-divider"></div>
    <div class="fm-gr-option">
      <div class="fm-gr-label">Shared node</div>
      <div class="fm-gr-device fm-gr-shared">
        <span class="fm-gr-icon">📡</span>
        <span class="fm-gr-name">Repeater + gateway</span>
        <div class="fm-gr-roles">
          <span class="fm-gr-role fm-gr-active">WiFi → MQTT</span>
          <span class="fm-gr-role fm-gr-active">RF relay</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fm-gr-arrow">↓</div>
      <div class="fm-gr-broker">MQTT broker</div>
      <div class="fm-gr-note">Two jobs: relay RF and report to the broker. Position is a compromise.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</figure>

<style>
  .fm-gateway-role {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .fm-gr-wrap {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: stretch;
    background: var(--surface-2, #f8f5f0);
    border: 1px solid var(--border, #d9d0c4);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .fm-gr-option {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .fm-gr-divider {
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--border, #d9d0c4);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .fm-gr-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text-muted, #7a6f62);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .fm-gr-device {
    background: var(--surface-1, #fff);
    border: 1px solid var(--border, #d9d0c4);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .fm-gr-icon {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .fm-gr-name {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text, #2d2620);
  }
  .fm-gr-roles {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }
  .fm-gr-role {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    display: inline-block;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .fm-gr-active {
    background: #d4edda;
    color: #1a5c2a;
  }
  .fm-gr-inactive {
    background: var(--surface-2, #f0ece6);
    color: var(--text-muted, #7a6f62);
    text-decoration: line-through;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .fm-gr-arrow {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted, #7a6f62);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .fm-gr-broker {
    background: var(--surface-1, #fff);
    border: 1px dashed var(--border, #d9d0c4);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text, #2d2620);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .fm-gr-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted, #7a6f62);
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
